<div class="well">
 <h2> <a href='/en/elliott-carter'>Elliott Carter</a> (1908-2012) </h2>

 <h1>
  <span>Concerto for orchestra</span>
  
    
    <span>(</span><span>1969</span><span></span><span>)</span>
    
  
</h1>




</div>

<div class="block-content">

