<div id="nomenclature">
  <b>Detailed formation</b>

  
  <ul><li>3 flutes (also 2 piccolos), 3 oboes (also English horn), 3 clarinets (also Eb clarinet, bass clarinet), 3 bassoons (also contrabassoon), 4 horns, 3 trumpets [une aussi en ré] , 3 trombones, tuba, timpani, 6 percussionists [à 8] , harp, piano, strings</li></ul>
</div>






